	Bring some ginger love into someone&rsquo;s life this Christmas and spoil them with this spicy scented winter warmer, with its rich lather and blend of festive myrrh and frankincense pure essential oils it&rsquo;s the gift that keeps on giving. &nbsp;This wonderful soap can be used like any normal bar of soap but is much milder. Simply rub the bar repeatedly between wet hands until you form a lather to clean your skin with or alternatively, rub the bar onto a sponge. This soap is also suitable for vegans. Due to the soap being hand made the pattern in the soap may vary slightly from the one pictured.</p>
